ockquote><br />\n最佳化呀 改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n化你老味，英式中文<br />\n<br />\n改善係最正確"},{"pid":"5e4c20a06bc84623a74063c86181ab35015572b2","tid":407182,"uid":33176,"like":39,"dislike":18,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T11:35:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>優化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ---&gt;改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最佳化呀 改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n化你老味，英式中文<br />\n<br />\n改善係最正確</blockquote><br />\n改善個改已經唔啱<br />\n有錯先要改<br />\noptimize應譯作&quot;微調達至效能提升&quot;<br />\n不過太累贅<br />\n唔好盲反，根本優化好好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f90671b2f4ae05ee0be822984a3fb8a9ed0e83ca","tid":407182,"uid":35706,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T12:28:42.000Z","msg":"優你老母化"},{"pid":"c559e5fbd1bfb164a5f451dd6facd880bc3aed86","tid":407182,"uid":36994,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T13:01:27.000Z","msg":"嗚 認錯都屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一陣開新post話改善 之後又話係叫優化架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba0fd8cd8731e67d1cfddf375dd7c9f8d4ca87c","tid":407182,"uid":48234,"like":27,"dislike":6,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T13:40:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嗚 認錯都屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一陣開新post話改善 之後又話係叫優化架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/igFX0xc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FigFX0xc.gif&h=c211a873&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你講效能改善或者最佳化冇人會屌<br />\n講優化呢個支那蝗語就一撚定屌<br />\n唔撚想俾人屌就改撚左佢以後咪撚用<br />\n驚唔撚記得就save左我嘅gif</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f689e7d81990483ffb466135e5a78cfaf9df8f0d","tid":407182,"uid":73695,"like":18,"dislike":22,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T14:45:45.000Z","msg":"你老母就蝗語, 2000年睇本地電腦雜誌已經用緊優化呢個詞語<br />\n你邊度有證據證明呢個字係出自蝗國? 唔好係蝗國見到呢個字就屈佢係蝗字<br />\n根本好多大陸用開的字都係出自香港, XX化呢類字本身就係香港叫開的<br />\n成班小學生未見過以前本地中文字就唔好以為乜9係大陸原創<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b95eaca282e451cffa4cbd043f21f29d3597aa20","tid":407182,"uid":126083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T14:49:02.000Z","msg":"裝咗個話係gtx Titan xp嘅軟件落gtx 550到<br />\n依家同Titan 一樣快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 建議裝埋100GB RAM軟件落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc954e6d3e4c812f4e8551eeca4dd0cf3d6bfd4","tid":407182,"uid":13173,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T14:55:05.000Z","msg":"點解唔用得XX化（最佳化）？呢啲西方學術term"},{"pid":"8eebaae73a8a99f7964cdc313b9941cd7ab98bb4","tid":407182,"uid":3987,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T15:00:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>優化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ---&gt;改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最佳化呀 改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最佳化聽落其實都有d問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點為之最佳?"},{"pid":"643bdd7277d1d94df5fe669bdc46cc6cefb0a619","tid":407182,"uid":73695,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T15:04:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔用得XX化（最佳化）？呢啲西方學術term</blockquote><br />\n冇人阻止你用最佳化呢個字<br />\n我只係想問幾時開始優化會