e":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T18:45:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你老母就蝗語, 2000年睇本地電腦雜誌已經用緊優化呢個詞語<br />\n你邊度有證據證明呢個字係出自蝗國? 唔好係蝗國見到呢個字就屈佢係蝗字<br />\n根本好多大陸用開的字都係出自香港, XX化呢類字本身就係香港叫開的<br />\n成班小學生未見過以前本地中文字就唔好以為乜9係大陸原創<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中文解毒"},{"pid":"9dad74a8aa0c966068c50966a21b65f2119134ff","tid":407182,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T18:47:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解唔用得XX化（最佳化）？呢啲西方學術term</blockquote><br />\n冇人阻止你用最佳化呢個字<br />\n我只係想問幾時開始優化會變左蝗語?<br />\n我記憶中優化呢個字最少十幾年前已經出現係本地的紙媒<br />\n因為大陸人用得多所以變成蝗語?<br />\n如果係咁, 大陸人叫GUNDAM跟香港人一樣叫高達, 咁我地又要唔要轉番?</blockquote><br />\n十幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咪回歸左lo on9仔<br />\n你係金庸份明報見到優化先講野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74be76afa3d6ed896be11defefdae6bde097bfdb","tid":407182,"uid":137647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T19:02:22.000Z","msg":"優化，內顯外顯，張display， display card,張graphic, 顯示卡，內置顯，外置顯<br />\n<br />\n好耐之前已經有用開同聽人用過<br />\n2000年左右，果陣自己開始砌機<br />\n<br />\n另外有人話用「提升」就真係無聽過<br />\n提升xxx效能就有<br />\n就咁用提升反而怪，提升d咩野？"},{"pid":"b81e3ae3adacfe49f7d6612f6ee9c0df679f214d","tid":407182,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T19:35:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e6adc092fd8239084731198bf6cb3f1b2ad32aa","tid":407182,"uid":72593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T20:09:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>加RAM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://downloadmoreram.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdownloadmoreram.com%2F&d=O4zg5sAizOM5IVs%2B7QnJGk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=5a8a07ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://downloadmoreram.com/</a></blockquote><br />\n有咩用？真係會當你加咗條ram定點？"},{"pid":"79a0e7b2a68056b5b6504f1f746d4aa09966b2ec